release_note: 1. Optimized some functions and fixed some bugs
1. Optimized some functions and fixed some bugs

1. The line spacing of the text can be modified now 2. Notebooks and PDFs added left and right scrolling browsing 3. To prevent accidental touch of the card double clicking on the card can be set to focus 4. Support for redirecting hyperlinks in PDF 5. Fixed a bug in iOS 17 where the settings button would disappear 6. Optimization of other functions
1. UI interface added dark mode 2. Optimized some functions and fixed some bugs

1. Optimized the issue of handwriting note jitter in laptops and PDFs 2. Fixed a bug where the format of the text box may change when zooming in or out 3. Optimized the issue of excessive image lag in laptops and PDFs 4. Optimized other functions and fixed some bugs
1. Import files in Word PowerPoint and other text formats which can be automatically converted to PDF format 2. Optimized some functions and fixed some bugs

1. Optimized the issue of canvas sliding during writing 2. Fixed the issue of PDF export and note cropping offset 3. The text and images added in PDF and notebook can be locked 4. In PDFs and notebooks alignment function has been added for text box and image movement 5. The PDF on the whiteboard can be split into images and the size of the split can be selected 6. The page order in the notebook can be changed now 7. Fixed known bugs
1. Fixed a bug where PDF files disappear after being deleted from the whiteboard and added to another whiteboard 2. Optimized some functions
1. Export whiteboard as PDF and optimize images 2. Fix bug in note direction error during PDF export 3. Local videos can be added to laptops and PDFs 4. Repair blank bugs when opening the notebook
1. Fixed some bugs

1. The hierarchical relationship between background boards can be adjusted mutually 2. Split PDF into image size adjustment 3. Notebooks and PDFs can be exported as images 4. Fix note misalignment caused by locking ratio in notebooks 5. Fixed known bugs and optimized some functions
1. Fix known bugs 2. Optimized some functions
1. Fixed issues with large pages being unable to write and delayed writing in laptops and PDFs

1. Add webpage snapshots link jumps and recordings to the notebook 2. Several new templates have been added to the notebook and external templates can also be imported 3. New lockdown ratio for laptops 4. Add page button in the upper right corner of the notebook 5. Add the function of copying the current page in notebooks and PDFs 6. Laptop Add Pull Up Add Page 7. PDF added calculator and timer and added finger drawing mode 8. A card with a screenshot of the video floating window which can be reversed to the frame of the video 9. Optimized text amplification and blurring in whiteboard 10. Fix known bugs
1. Add notebook mode 2. Fix known bugs

1. Add a timer on the whiteboard which can count forward and down. 2. Add handwriting data backup function in PDF and each page will automatically save the last ten handwriting data. 3. The thumbnail in the PDF can now display handwritten notes. 4. A ruler can be used in PDF now. 5. Search in the upper left corner of the whiteboard add handwritten note classification and quickly locate the first and last handwritten notes. 6. Fix known bugs.

1. The background board can be set to a default size such as A4 size 2. Cropped excerpts in PDF can now include handwritten notes or they can be set to not include 3. The lasso has been re equipped with replication and straightening functions 4. Fix known bugs

1. Lasso optimization in whiteboard and PDF 2. In PDF you can use a lasso to select handwritten notes and change their size 3. Handwritten notes that can be pasted and copied by long pressing in PDF 4. Fix known bugs

1. Link jump allows adding external links 2. The default style can be set for the background board 3. The recording on the whiteboard can be exported now 4. Add a simple calculator to the whiteboard 5. Optimized the sensitivity of finger long press selection for text in PDF 6. Optimized the issue of blurry handwritten notes exported in PDF 7. Optimization of heating when using the APP 8. Fix known bugs

1. Add OCR to recognize text in images 2. Two types of stickers and solid colors have been added to the tape background and whether to display a shadow switch has been added to the tape menu 3. Pages can be added or deleted in PDF now 4. Added eraser in PDF to clear current page function 5. Add translation function in PDF 6. The pencil case can be dragged to the top now 7. The thumbnails on the whiteboard can be layered Add a pushpin link which allows you to quickly open the whiteboard where the pushpin is located from an external app through the link

1. All operations on the whiteboard can be redo and undo and Laser pointer and tape can be redo and undo in PDF 2. The deleted PDF can be restored in the recycle bin 3. Pens that are not frequently used in the pen box can be hidden 4. Whiteboard search for pushpin list long press and drag to sort pushpins 5. The connection line can save default parameters now 6. Add Message Center 7. Fix known bugs

1. The content in the background board can be moved along with it or individually 2. Long press on the whiteboard to call up the shortcut menu bar Paste Text Image Pushpin Link Jump . You can paste the copied data and quickly create text cards image cards Pushpins Link Jump at the specified location 3. Support reading fonts from imported devices 4. The file type supports using a floating window to open and browse 5. Tape can be used in PDF now 6. Multiple outlines can be created on one page in PDF 7. PDF supports cropping and extracting images

1. The thickness of the Laser pointer can be adjusted 2. Laser pointer notes can also be permanently saved in PDF 3. The notes and annotations in PDF can be exported together with PDF 4. After selecting handwritten notes on the whiteboard with a lasso they can be resized 5. In the Eraser menu the one button screen clearing function is added
